===Format===
* '''Holi Face-Off''' : ''March 23rd - 24th
** 16 teams.
** 2 matchdays
* '''Day 1''' : ''March 23rd
** 16 teams will play ''Payload mode.
** 4 matches
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} qualify for ''Arena Battle'' on ''Day 2.
* '''Day 2''' : ''March 24th
** 8 teams
** Arena mode
** Single-elimination bracket
** All matches are Best-of-1. Final is Best-of-3

===Points System===
{{PUBGM 2021 Points System}}
* Teams will get 3 points for each finish secured in Match 2 and 4.

